1.5
log
@Implement dl_iterate_phdr() for static PIE executables using info extracted
from the aux vector.

ok patrick@@ kettenis@@
@
text
@/*	$OpenBSD: init.c,v 1.4 2016/05/07 19:05:22 guenther Exp $ */
/*
